===Etymology===
From Latin ''[[localitas]]''.

===Noun===
'''locality'''
#The fact or quality of having a [[position]] in [[space]].
#''pl'' The [[feature]]s or [[surroundings]] of a particular [[place]].
#The [[situation]] or [[position]] of an [[object]].
#An [[area]] or [[district]] considered as the [[site]] of certain [[activity|activities]]; a [[neighbourhood]].

